trans-unit.source: Represents a single relationship between an object and a member.
trans-unit.target: Rappresenta una singola relazione tra un oggetto e un membro.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationshipService> is used by a serializer to announce that one property is related to a property on another object.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationshipService> viene utilizzato da un serializzatore di annunciare che una proprietà è correlata a una proprietà su un altro oggetto.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship> represents a single relationship between an object and a member that <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationshipService> uses in its interactions with a serializer.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship> rappresenta una singola relazione tra un oggetto e un membro che <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationshipService> Usa nelle proprie interazioni con un serializzatore.

trans-unit.source: The object that owns <c>member</c>.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto a cui appartiene <c>member</c>.

trans-unit.source: The member which is to be related to <c>owner</c>.
trans-unit.target: Il membro da correlare a <c>owner</c>.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inizializza una nuova istanza della classe <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" />.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="owner" /> or <paramref name="member" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="owner" /> o <paramref name="member" /> è <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: Represents the empty member relationship.
trans-unit.target: Rappresenta la relazione di membri vuota.

trans-unit.source: This field is read-only.
trans-unit.target: Questo campo è di sola lettura.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship> structure is empty if neither the owner nor the member is assigned.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship> struttura è vuota se il proprietario né il membro viene assegnato.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> to compare with the current <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" />.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> da confrontare con l'oggetto <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> corrente.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether two <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> instances are equal.
trans-unit.target: Determina se due istanze di <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> sono uguali.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the specified <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> is equal to the current <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se l'oggetto <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> specificato è uguale all'oggetto <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> corrente; in caso contrario, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Returns the hash code for this instance.
trans-unit.target: Restituisce il codice hash per l'istanza.

trans-unit.source: A hash code for the current <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" />.
trans-unit.target: Codice hash per l'oggetto <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> corrente.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether this relationship is equal to the <see cref="F:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.Empty" /> relationship.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene un valore che indica se questa relazione è uguale alla relazione <see cref="F:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.Empty" />.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if this relationship is equal to the <see cref="F:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.Empty" /> relationship; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se questa relazione è uguale alla relazione <see cref="F:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.Empty" />; in caso contrario, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the related member.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene il membro correlato.

trans-unit.source: The member that is passed in to the <see cref="M:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.#ctor(System.Object,System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor)" />.
trans-unit.target: Membro passato al metodo <see cref="M:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.#ctor(System.Object,System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor)" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> structure that is to the left of the equality operator.
trans-unit.target: Struttura <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> a sinistra dell'operatore di uguaglianza.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> structure that is to the right of the equality operator.
trans-unit.target: Struttura <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> a destra dell'operatore di uguaglianza.

trans-unit.source: Tests whether two specified <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> structures are equivalent.
trans-unit.target: Verifica se due strutture <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> specificate sono equivalenti.

trans-unit.source: This operator returns <see langword="true" /> if the two <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> structures are equal; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: Questo operatore restituisce <see langword="true" /> se le due strutture <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> sono uguali, in caso contrario restituisce <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The equivalent method for this operator is <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.Equals%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
trans-unit.target: Il metodo equivalente per l'operatore è <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.Equals%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> structure that is to the left of the inequality operator.
trans-unit.target: Struttura <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> a sinistra dell'operatore di disuguaglianza.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> structure that is to the right of the inequality operator.
trans-unit.target: Struttura <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> a destra dell'operatore di disuguaglianza.

trans-unit.source: Tests whether two specified <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> structures are different.
trans-unit.target: Verifica se due strutture <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> specificate sono diverse.

trans-unit.source: This operator returns <see langword="true" /> if the two <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> structures are different; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: Questo operatore restituisce <see langword="true" /> se le due strutture <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship" /> sono diverse, in caso contrario restituisce <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The equivalent method for this operator is <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.Equals%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
trans-unit.target: Il metodo equivalente per l'operatore è <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.Equals%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the owning object.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene l'oggetto proprietario.

trans-unit.source: The owning object that is passed in to the <see cref="M:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.#ctor(System.Object,System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor)" />.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto proprietario passato al metodo <see cref="M:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.MemberRelationship.#ctor(System.Object,System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor)" />.
